    "valueRenamed": "\u201c{old}\u201d renamed to \u201c{n}\u201d",
    "cannotDeleteLastOption": "Cannot delete the last option",
    "valueDeletedQ": "\u201c{val}\u201d deleted",
    "cselEditValuePrompt": "ແກ້ໄຂຄ່າ:",
    "deleteValueFromListQ": "ລຶບ \"{val}\" ອອກຈາກລາຍການນີ້ບໍ?",
    "kitchenSidebarHint": "ໜ້າທີ່ຄົວ: ເປີດເມນູ ☰ ເພື່ອໃຊ້ແຖບຂ້າງ.",
